<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>Ben-Hur Santos Ott</title><link>https://benhurott.com</link><description>AI Agents Security | AppSec | DevSecOps</description><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 07:20:00 GMT</pubDate><lastBuildDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 12:22:59 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>marmite</generator><image><url>https://benhurott.com/media/img/og-banner.jpg</url><title></title><link></link></image><item><title>Run Claude Code using Ollama</title><link>https://benhurott.com/claude-ollama.html</link><description><![CDATA["This tutorial shows how to run claude code using a local Ollama model."]]></description><author>ben-hur</author><category>ollama</category><category>claude</category><guid>https://benhurott.com/claude-ollama.html</guid><pubDate>Mon, 30 Mar 2026 07:20:00 GMT</pubDate><source url="https://benhurott.com">archive-2026</source><content:encoded><![CDATA[<!-- Content Injected to every content markdown header -->
<p>Install Ollama:</p>
<pre><code class="language-sh">curl -fsSL https://ollama.com/install.sh | sh
</code></pre>
<p>Pull a model</p>
<pre><code class="language-sh">ollama pull llama3.2
</code></pre>
<p>Configure the ollama select model for claude</p>
<pre><code class="language-sh">ollama launch claude --model llama3.2
</code></pre>
<p>Set the env vars to connect Claude to Ollama:</p>
<pre><code class="language-sh">export ANTHROPIC_AUTH_TOKEN=&quot;ollama&quot;
export ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=&quot;&quot;
export ANTHROPIC_BASE_URL=&quot;http://localhost:11434&quot;
</code></pre>
<p>Run claude</p>
<pre><code class="language-sh">claude --model llama3.2
</code></pre>
